            "text": " the filesystem can't support many other <i>interesting</i> features that you might not even think to ask for because the existing tools are too limited, cross-index the files based on shared structures for easy searches, hyperlinking, complex filesystem queries (i.e. other than 'find <regexp>'), joins, etc.",
